description:
For use with the FoodSaver vacuum sealing system, FoodSaver rolls are used to lock in the freshness and preserve the life of your food. The rolls can be used in the fridge, freezer or microwave and to simmer food in a pan. You can use the rolls to create custom sized bags for vacuum sealing your food.

Made of patented, heavy-duty 5-ply material with special channels that enable the efficient and complete removal of air. Prevents freezer burn.

Locks out air and moisture. Seals in freshness. Unique design maximises air removal. Preserves food flavour. Each roll measures 550 x 28cm.

  • BPA free.

description:
The Ohio high sleeper packs an all-in-one punch with its built-in wardrobe, shelves, drawers and desk. Study, store, play and sleep - no further furniture required. Boom! Space saving and money saving, it's also a solid bit of kit designed to last a while. Featuring a sturdy wooden frame, this versatile bunk comes with a durable ladder for safe and easy access. And the drawers boast smooth-gliding metal runners.

Comes with a medium feel Young Airsprung Kids mattress (8883535), a foam free open coil mattress that doesn't need turning. It is soft and supportive for a good night's sleep, and also has a smooth anti allergy knit cover for peace of mind.

Your kid will love this bed. Ideal for any age over 6 years, up to a max weight of 100kg, they're not going to grow out of it quickly! We suggest at least 2 people put it together - it's easy enough to assemble but being solid it is pretty heavy.

Sleeper:

  • Shorty bed.
  • Self-assembly - 2 people recommended.
  • If this product is over 60cm high it must be securely attached to the wall to prevent overturning.
  • Ladder is in a fixed position.
  • Maximum user weight per bunk 100kg.
  • For ages 6 years and over.

Mattress:

  • Medium feel mattress.
  • Open coil mattress with 192 springs.
  • Knit cover with flat top finish.
  • Anti allergy.
  • Easy care no turn mattress.
  • Requires Young Airsprungmattress - 1 mattress (included).
  • Safety tested to 100kg.
  • Maximum depth of mattress to be used is 16cm.

Dimensions:

  • Frame size L180, W80, H150cm.
  • Mattress size L175, W75, D16cm.
  • Clearance between floor and underside of bed 115cm.
title: Argos Home Ohio Beech Shorty High Sleeper & Kids Mattress

description:
ReCap Fermentation Kits wanted a low-profile, waterless airlock that had an authentic one-way valve to let gases escape and absolutely not let air in. Something that eliminated the need to monitor the fermenting jars every day, but made it easy to peek in and taste when desired. We wanted something that could easily convert to plain storage to put in the refrigerator when complete. The reCAP Fermenter makes fermentation AND storage easier and more fun.

Fermented foods are very easy to make at home. Along with being cost-effective it's actually better to make your own. Store-bought options are usually pasteurized, which kills good bacteria. Some of the best fermented foods for promoting gut health.

The popular recap fermenter keeps the oxygen from entering the jar and allows the bubbles (co2) to escape. Thousands of people have successfully learned how to ferment at home using the recap system. Each kit includes free downloadable recipes and tips.

description:
This Candy Heat Pump Condensor tumble dryer does not require an external wall vent. The condensed water is collected in a container ready for emptying. With NFC features you can use a smartphone to control monitor and manage your appliance. Other features include KG detector and specialist programmes specific for all your delicate garments.

A heat pump integrated condensor dryer provides high energy efficiency. The heat pump technology heats the air without an electrical heater and extracts moisture from the clothes, transforming water into steam, allowing you to reduce the energy consumption. By working at a lower temprature it also takes full expert care of all your fabrics.

NFC Smart Touch works as simply as a contactless payment system. By using an Android or smartphone you can control, monitor and manage your appliance via your mobile. The cycle function allows you to download additional programmes as well as using the smart check-up to check the appliance and ensure it is working efficiently as possible.

The clever kg detector uses a sensor to weigh the load early in a cycle, then adjusts the time, water and electricity to suit, so you get effective cleaning while using the smallest amount of water and electricity possible - this gives an A+ rating for energy efficiency.

Overview:

description:
A heat pump integrated condensor dryer provides high energy efficiency. The heat pump technology heats the air without an electrical heater and extracts moisture from the clothes, transforming water into steam, allowing you to reduce the energy consumption. By working at a lower temprature it also takes full expert care of all your fabrics.

NFC Smart Touch works as simply as a contactless payment system. By using an Android or smartphone you can control, monitor and manage your appliance via your mobile. The cycle function allows you to download additional programmes as well as using the smart check-up to check the appliance and ensure it is working efficiently as possible.

The clever kg detector uses a sensor to weigh the load early in a cycle, then adjusts the time, water and electricity to suit, so you get effective cleaning while using the smallest amount of water and electricity possible - this gives an A+ rating for energy efficiency.

description:
The Bose Home Speaker 500 delivers wall-to-wall stereo sound from a single speaker. Built-in voice control from Alexa puts songs, playlists, and more at the tip of your tongue. And you have the freedom to control the music your way — with your voice, with a tap on the top controls, or with the Bose Music app.

Play. Pause. Shuffle. Or skip to your favourite song. You'll have millions of playlists, albums and more at the tip of your tongue. With Alexa built in, you have access to things like weather reports and news headlines, too. So if you want to hear something, just ask. And future software updates will add new features.

Turning the music up at a party? It's not a problem for our voice pickup technology. Just under the surface is a custom-designed eight-microphone array, so the speaker still hears you, even when it gets loud. You can turn off voice access whenever you want, too. Just tap the microphone off button to cut power to all microphones and continue to access the other features of the speaker.

Control doesn't stop at just voice. You can tap the top controls to play, pause or skip tracks, or manage it all from the Bose Music app. And you can set up to six different presets for playlists, Internet radio stations and more, so your favourites are just a tap away.

description:
Dixit is the lovingly illustrated game of creative guesswork where your imagination unlocks the tale. Use the beautiful imagery on your cards to bluff your opponents and guess which image matches the story. Guessing right is only half the battle – to succeed, you must get your friends to decide that your card tells the story. Suitable for 3 to 6 players.

Dixit is a ground-breaking game, featuring high-quality components and breath taking artwork and offering delightful and thought-provoking entertainment for all your friends and family.

Add dreams, journeys and quests with various expansions that add more artwork and themes to the game.

Dixit won the Spiel de Jahres award for game design in 2010 with its brilliant and simple gameplay, beautiful and imaginative design, and the possibility of creating fun for all.

Dixit is a wonderfully simple game, playable by nearly anyone with whom you share a common language.

Use your flair and intuition to select the right image while avoiding the pitfalls set by the other players.

This Hoover AXI Washer Dryer has a 10kg washing capacity, a 6kg drying capacity and an impressive 1600rpm spin speed. It comes with 11 washing programmes and 3 drying programmes. The washing side features a full load programme in 59 minutes and three further rapid washes in 44 minutes or less. The drying side has three drying programmes offering you a choice of the best care for your garments.

Care Dose- You have the option to auto-dose your washing load with liquid detergent. Care Dose will automatically dose your washing loads with liquid detergent and softener- this method doses each load correct to 1ml, and will save you money and prevent your load from over exposure to excessive detergent This will automatically dose your load, for an average of 18 cycles.

Wifi- You can connect your Smartphone to the machine, in a similar way to contactless card payment. This will allow you to download additional programmes and run diagnostics checks on the machine. To find out all about how this can transform your laundry day, watch the handy videos on this page.

All in One- Our customers love this feature! Full load capacity in 59 minutes, allowing you to wash any colour together in less than an hour, with the same brilliant results.

description:
Introducing the Sony WF-1000XM3 premium wireless noise cancelling headphones. Packed with industry-leading technology, an ergonomic design and more stable Bluetooth connection, the WF1000XM3 give you a remarkable sound that you can enjoy without a wire in sight. Sony recommends you always update your devices with their latest available software. Software update notifications for WF-1000XM3, and the updates themselves, are delivered via the Sony Headphones Connect app, available free of charge on the Google Play and Apple App Store.

The brand new industry-leading QN1e processor boosts the range of frequencies from which noise-cancellation occurs, giving you full control over the sounds you want to block out whilst listening to your music. That means it's never been easier to take the bustle out of travel and immerse yourself in sound.

The WF1000XM3 comes with Adaptive Sound Control to optimise listening settings automatically based on your behaviour and environment. This can be customised to suit your own preferences, using the equaliser from the Sony Headphone Connect app (works with android and iOS).

Up to 8 hours on a single charge when not using noise cancellation, or 6 hours with noise cancellation. The earbuds come with a stylish portable carrying case, which give an additional three charges! And if you're in a hurry, you can get 90 minutes use after just 10 minute of charge.

  • Padded ear pieces.
  • Detachable cable.
  • Foldable.
  • In-line with microphone for calls and track control controls.
  • Adjustable headband.
  • 40mm driver.
  • Carry case.
  • 10m range.
  • Compatible with universal smartphones.
  • Batteries required 1 x rechargeable battery (included) .
  • Rechargeable battery.
  • 30 hour battery life.
  • 180 minute charging time.
  • In the box: Carrying Case, Plug Adaptor for In-flight Use, Headphone cable (approx. 1.2m) USB Cable: Type-C (approx. 20 cm).

  • EAN: 4548736088818.
  • Warning - Not suitable for children under the age of 3 years due to small parts and entanglement hazard.

description:
Car Mechanic Simulator is your one stop car mechanic shop that challenges you to find, repair, paint, tune, sell and test drive cars!

Release date: 25 June 2019.

This item is FREE delivery.

  • Suitable for the Xbox One.



Construct and expand your car renovation kingdom in this hyper-realistic simulation experience. With each mission offering its own unique criteria, varying difficulty and time constraints to meet, Car Mechanic Simulator will test the mettle of your inner grease-monkey. Featuring a cornucopia of cars (48), a ton of tools (10+) and a prodigious plethora of parts (1000+), what are you waiting for? It's time to roll up your sleeves and get to work!

With state of the art, photorealistic graphics and an incredible level of attention to detail, gearheads will be in seventh-heaven and player progression will permit the upgrade of the garage, allowing the addition of specific equipment such as the lacquer sprayer or a parts warehouse. Discover a true junkyard jewel or find a forgotten beauty gathering dust in a barn, and then unleash your imagination and restore these classics to their former glory.

Car Mechanic Simulator also includes car auctions where old cars are available for resale or can be purchased for your collection. It will be up to you to find the perfect deal! And luckily you will have access to a multi-level carpark to store all your 4-wheeled wonders! The game's infinite number of randomly generated missions will keep you more than busy (and greasy! ).

  • For ages 3 years and over.
  • EAN: 4020628778798.

description:
Sleep Tight All Night is a versatile 4 in 1 product that has been specially designed to help teach children when to sleep and when it's time to get up - aiding the transition from cot to bed. It offers a unique sleep aid system that has been based on scientific studies relating to the colours associated with inhibiting and encouraging sleep. Also fully adaptable for daytime play and an ideal travel companion, this innovative new product will become a must have for parents whilst offering a fun solution for children to enjoy.

Set the timer for the duration you would ideally like your child to sleep; with a full nights sleep or just a quick nap.

A gentle squeeze of the tummy will help your child get to sleep, using soothing sounds and red glowing light. The red light indicates to your child that it's still night time.

Awake during the night? A tummy squeeze will help comfort your child using soothing sounds and red glowing light. When the tummy is squeezed after the pre-set time is reached it will glow green to indicate it's time to get up Play Time.

In day mode, squeeze the tummy during the daytime play for fun character phrases The sleep aid module that fits neatly within the body has the following features Sleep mode with timer.

A choice of 5 soothing sounds including; falling raindrops, soothing surf, gentle heartbeat, whispering waterfall and comforting crickets. The module can also be set to no sounds, if preferred.

description:
From the creators of Tower of Guns, MOTHERGUNSHIP mixes bullet-hell intensity with the FPS genre, and promises you one of the largest gun customization options seen in video games. It's up to you to equip your over-the-top arsenal and defeat a robotic alien armada that has conquered Earth.

Craft gun monstrosities that no reasonable person could ever lift, play together with your friends, fight gigantic bosses and experience randomized mayhem as you battle your way to the heart of the fleet to destroy the MOTHERGUNSHIP!

Release date: tbc 2018.

This item is FREE delivery.

  • Suitable for the PS4.



CRAFT: To take down the MOTHERGUNSHIP, you'll need your very own, personalized weapons of destruction. Luckily you can create the gun of your dreams with one of the most modular gun-crafting systems ever seen in a videogame. Want to have a twelve-barrel gun that shoots homing rockets? Or do you prefer a lightning shotgun? And what gun wouldn't look better with a fish tank affixed to the top? Go for it! The design of your destructive arsenal is in your hands!


FIGHT: Face off against overwhelming odds in brutal, non-stop combat, where thinking on your feet is the only way to survive. Dodge hundreds of bullets with unique FPS/Bullet-hell hybrid gameplay. Each ship hosts hordes of alien machines, deadly traps, and intimidating bosses, all set on preventing you from saving humanity. Go get 'em.

RESIST: Join the ranks of the global resistance movement and take back Earth together with your friends. Fight together with a friend in a full co-op experience, or participate with the community while you work together to cut through the alien fleet and reach that ultimate goal - bringing down the MOTHERGUNSHIP.

  • For ages 12 years and over.

description:
Discover a new world without boundaries in the 6.09 inch Dewdrop HD plus display. This wide screen with a 87 percent screen-to-body ratio provides a greater view for your videos, photos and favourite books. The HUAWEI Y6 2019 also blocks out harmful blue light and is TUV Rheinland certified. The 8 MP front facing camera on the HUAWEI Y6 2019 paired up with an advanced Selfie Toning Flash 2.0, a front flash toning light assisted by screen light, enables you to capture a true, natural and accurate portrait even in low light conditions.

Capture greatness with the 13 MP rear camera. The wide f1.8 aperture lens lets in 50 percent more light to enhance the quality and clarity in your low-light shots.

The HUAWEI Y6 2019 can release an additional 6db of sound with stronger bass effects. This phone is your personal portable speaker while listening to music at home, partying with friends or hanging out at the beach.

The 12nm chipset and 2 plus 32 GB expandable large memory of the HUAWEI Y6 2019 can store all of your content and has the ability to multitask smoothly.

The HUAWEI Y6 2019 leverages a 3020 mAh battery with intelligent battery optimization. The software with hardware synergy works together to keep your phone going all day long.

Model number: Y6 2019 Black.

Network:

  • Network provider: Sim free.
  • 2G, 3G and 4G network capability.
  • SIM card type: nano SIM.

Display and Design:

  • 6.09 inch LCD display.
  • Resolution 1560 x 720 pixels.
  • Touch screen.
  • Toughened glass.

Dimensions:

  • Size H156.28, W73.5, D59mm.
  • Weight 150g.

Camera and Video:

  • Front camera 8MP.
  • Rear camera 13MP.
  • Led.
  • Camera features: Ambient light, proximity sensor, Selfie toning, face unlock.
  • Video capture in 1080p HD quality.

Storage:

  • Internal memory 32GB.
  • Expandable memory up to 512GB when using microSD card slot. Boost your storage to hold more tunes, holiday snaps and extra apps.

Technical specifications:

  • 2GHz quad core Quad-Core Processor processor.
  • 2GB RAM.
  • Operating system: Android 9.

Battery:

  • Up to 437 hours standby time.
  • Up to 1440 minutes talk time.
  • 3020mAh battery capacity.

Product features:

  • MP3 and MP4 player.
  • Headphone port.
  • This phone features fast charge technology - faster than standard charging, for when time is of the essence.
  • Contactless payment Link up your card to your phone for easy buying on purchases up to £30.
  • Fingerprint scanner For simple, safe and speedy unlocking and better security.

Connectivity:

  • Wi-Fi.
  • Bluetooth.
  • NFC.
  • GPS.

General information:

  • EAN: 6901443289189.
